snippet.title: QuizMi Trailer
snippet.description:
QuizMi - A brand new quiz trivia mobile game that builds on the legacy of QuizUp and brings a fresh take on the genre.

Play against others worldwide with exciting multiplayer features, challenge your knowledge with a variety of categories and questions, and experience the excitement of a brand new quiz trivia game. Subscribe to get the latest updates on the game's development!
